alphabetical; and each stanza begins with a letter of the Hebrew
alphabet in regular order, till we come to <span
id="xxix.ii-p3.1"></span>[Ps
145:14](../../../bib/kjv/psa145.htm#014.md)<span id="xxix.ii-p3.1"></span>,
